If you are a monopolist

00:44:41.000 --> 00:44:44.000
and you have three to five main competitors,

00:44:44.000 --> 00:44:47.000
you have to enter into a conspiracy

00:44:47.000 --> 00:44:50.000
to become a monopolist through a conspiracy

00:44:50.000 --> 00:44:53.000
and to achieve a higher standard of the added value.

